### Checklist

Make sure all of these items are complete, or else the PR will be ineligible for a code review.

- [ ] Code passes all existing [tests](https://github.com/sendgrid/sendgrid-php/tree/master/test/unit)
- [ ] Any new functionality added includes new unit tests
- [ ] Create or update example code to show the new functionality in action.
- [ ] All code, branch, and git naming and style conventions are followed (see [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](https://github.com/sendgrid/sendgrid-php/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#style-guidelines--naming-conventions))
- [ ] Feature branch has been rebased off of the latest `master` branch. ( see [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](https://github.com/sendgrid/sendgrid-php/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#creating-a-pull-request)).